Name: DeliverwarTH
About the game: This game is an online First person shooter game. In the game there will be two teams for you to choose from, that is. orange delivery and green delivery In each game map, there will be weapons for you to choose from. You can choose your class before choosing a room to play. The playing mode system is as follows. - team deathmatch Kill an opposing player - free for all Kill all players in the game. - capture the flag hoist the flag of the opposite side You can increase or decrease the number of bots before starting the game.
